Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现的太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 蜜蕾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到沃尔夫少校信号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现证据！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎·穆莱中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从现在起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在菲利特·明日野中将的指挥下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长外出时 本舰指挥由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行使联邦军权限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取设施控制权
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中的机动战士队 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动机动战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然发现与维甘私下勾结的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的居民区进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会造成很多无辜伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动机动战士不是唯一的解决办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人征求你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不歼灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤亡会进一步扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该考虑把牺牲控制在最小限度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是你说了算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是身为指挥官的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:13:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间的迟疑 可能导致无法挽回的恶果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜牺牲市民…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会服从这样的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士队的指挥由奥布莱特中尉负责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adele装备TITUS装备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是高达的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆那家伙 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎 走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是被逼的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘威胁我们 迫不得已…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保全索伦城 只能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蕾丝 上车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我必须去安排工人避难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我去完成自己最后的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子压根儿没打算乖乖投降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经打到这种地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到这种情形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸还会说那种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打败维甘 这是不得已？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 你说得都对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家谁不难过？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令一定也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信 杰哈特和你战斗时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再有迷茫 干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不难过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙终究是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎她们情况不妙 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不歼灭敌人 伤亡会进一步扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间的迟疑 可能带来无法挽回的恶果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把坐标发给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用自动驾驶放出AGE2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想伤害你 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 只为保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是决不能拱手让出这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会耍大牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁死不肯交出情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 善后已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认维甘男子死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 物证全部销毁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在小黑屋里关一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有东西想给他看呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出去感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是无法执行那种命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这么当兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为男人也不光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是坐上了高达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只能在战斗中寻求答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空停下脚步烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该超越的既不是老爸也不是别的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古鲁迪克舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了 菲利特
